It's heartfelt songs like these that make me think why modern Indian Bollywood music can never compete to it. Because the lyrics are so pure, the rhythm is so moving, the voice is so touching and the meaning...SubhanAllah !! While the trash makers here like Honey Shit and Mika Shit continue to plague our ears with their so-called "music", I sincerely thank Pakistan for this one gem of a song. Please never change the soulfulness of your music. 
Applause and tremendous respect from an Indian fan. #MusicNeedsNoBoundaries
